Question 6:
Define a class in Java to accept the names of 10 cities in a single-dimension string array and their STD (Subscriber Trunk Dialing) codes in another single-dimension integer array.
Search for the name of a city input by the user in the list.

If found, display "Search Successful" and print the name of the city along with its STD code.
Otherwise, display "Search Unsuccessful, No such city in the list."